<C>__{mrs. murchak}
<D>__{i used to love him. he was my little doll.}
<A>__{he turns the page. a picture of perry (6) and linda sitting on the back steps of a shack, poking with a stick at something in the dirt. after a moment, she gets up, clears coffee cups.}
